{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"407f94f5"},"source":["## 📝 Notebook Usage Guide\n","\n","This notebook is designed to guide you through the process of training a U-Net model for semantic segmentation of multispectral satellite images to **burned** and **unburned** classes. This notebook utilizes image patches generated in a previous step, either from the `Patch_creation` or `Merging_patches` notebooks. These patches serve as the input for training the U-Net model.\n","\n","To effectively use this notebook, follow these steps:\n","\n","1.  **Configuration**: Start by reviewing and adjusting the parameters in the '⚙️ Configuration' section. This includes setting your project directory, data paths, experiment names, and training hyperparameters.\n","2.  **Run All Cells**: The notebook is structured to be run sequentially. You can execute all cells by going to 'Runtime' > 'Run all' in the Colab menu.\n","3.  **Monitor Progress**: Pay attention to the output of cells, especially during data loading, model training, and evaluation. TensorBoard is integrated for visualizing training progress.\n","4.  **Review Visualizations**: The notebook includes several visualization steps for understanding data samples, model architecture, and prediction results. Ensure these plots are generated correctly.\n","5.  **Interpret Results**: After the model training and evaluation, review the test results, including loss, accuracy, and Mean IoU, both overall and per-class."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#⚙️ Configuration (set all the parameters)"],"metadata":{"id":"WIwX0ogZojYE"}},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"iMnhizE5b74H"},"outputs":[],"source":["project_dir = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/U-Net_burned_areas_project\" # Base directory for the project, where data, models, and experiments are stored.\n","\n","patches_folder_name = 'dataset_PS_SENT_432_682' # Name of the folder containing merged patches.\n","\n","patches_from_merged_dataset = True # Boolean flag: if True, patches are loaded from a merged dataset folder; otherwise, from a specific site's patches.\n","\n","specific_site_name = \"site-385-tropical-savanna\" # Name of a specific site. Only used if `patches_from_merged_dataset` is False, to load patches for this site only.\n","\n","experiment_name = f\"unet_{patches_folder_name}_whatever\" # A unique name for the current experiment, used for saving logs, models, and results.\n","\n","# Training hyperparameters of Neural network\n","BATCH_SIZE = 64 # Number of samples processed in each training iteration.\n","LEARNING_RATE = 1e-3 # Step size for the optimizer during training.\n","PATIENCE = 30 # Number of epochs to wait for improvement in validation metric before early stopping.\n","EPOCHS = 120 # Default 200 # Maximum number of training cycles.\n","SPLITS_SIZE = 300 # Size for splitting datasets (e.g., train/validation/test).\n","INPUT_SIZE = (128, 128)  # (Height, Width) # Spatial dimensions (height, width) of the input image patches.\n","NUM_WORKERS = 4 # Number of subprocesses to use for data loading, improving loading speed."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#⏳ Training of U-Net... (run all the cells)"],"metadata":{"id":"Mi3cAmswo10m"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"z6Ma47R9e5I6"},"source":["## 🌐 **Google Drive Connection**"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount(\"/content/drive\")\n","\n","%cd $project_dir"],"metadata":{"id":"Kv3LfRzKbVIb","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780848633589,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":1145,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"}},"outputId":"d81ab899-d579-41bb-e551-ee8f51f34cd5"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Drive already mounted at /content/drive; to attempt to forcibly remount, call drive.mount(\"/content/drive\", force_remount=True).\n","/content/drive/MyDrive/Geoinformatics_Project/NewStructure\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"QeG_QeUTfD0c"},"source":["## ⚙️ **Libraries Import**"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"collapsed":true,"id":"q7UvZ1XufEw2","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780848671672,"user_tz":-120,"elapsed":38085,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"}},"outputId":"fd6bed73-ebb8-4fad-eaa2-0eec59e4514b"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Collecting torchview\n","  Downloading torchview-0.2.7-py3-none-any.whl.metadata (13 kB)\n","Requirement already satisfied: graphviz in /usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages (from torchview) (0.21)\n","Downloading torchview-0.2.7-py3-none-any.whl (26 kB)\n","Installing collected packages: torchview\n","Successfully installed torchview-0.2.7\n","\u001b[2K   \u001b[90m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m \u001b[32m983.4/983.4 kB\u001b[0m \u001b[31m21.8 MB/s\u001b[0m eta \u001b[36m0:00:00\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[?25htorchmetrics version: 1.9.0\n","PyTorch version: 2.11.0+cu128\n","Device: cuda\n"]}],"source":["# Set seed for reproducibility\n","SEED = 42\n","\n","# Import necessary libraries\n","import os\n","import shutil\n","from pathlib import Path\n","from matplotlib.colors import ListedColormap\n","from matplotlib.patches import Patch\n","\n","# Set environment variables before importing modules\n","os.environ['PYTHONHASHSEED'] = str(SEED)\n","os.environ['MPLCONFIGDIR'] = os.getcwd() + '/configs/'\n","\n","# Suppress warnings\n","import warnings\n","warnings.simplefilter(action='ignore', category=FutureWarning)\n","warnings.simplefilter(action='ignore', category=Warning)\n","\n","# Import necessary modules\n","import logging\n","import random\n","import numpy as np\n","\n","# Set seeds for random number generators in NumPy and Python\n","np.random.seed(SEED)\n","random.seed(SEED)\n","\n","# Import PyTorch\n","import torch\n","torch.manual_seed(SEED)\n","from torch import nn\n","from torch.nn import functional as F\n","from torchsummary import summary\n","from torch.utils.tensorboard import SummaryWriter\n","import torchvision\n","from torchvision.transforms import v2 as transforms\n","from torch.utils.data import TensorDataset, DataLoader, Dataset\n","import math\n","import matplotlib.gridspec as gridspec\n","\n","!pip install torchview\n","from torchview import draw_graph\n","\n","# Install torchmetrics for native metrics\n","!pip install -q torchmetrics\n","import torchmetrics\n","print(f\"torchmetrics version: {torchmetrics.__version__}\")\n","\n","# Configure device and seeds\n","if torch.cuda.is_available():\n","    device = torch.device(\"cuda\")\n","    torch.cuda.manual_seed_all(SEED)\n","    torch.backends.cudnn.deterministic = True\n","    torch.backends.cudnn.benchmark = False\n","else:\n","    device = torch.device(\"cpu\")\n","# device = torch.device(\"cpu\")\n","\n","# Setup directories\n","logs_dir = \"tensorboard\"\n","!pkill -f tensorboard\n","%load_ext tensorboard\n","!mkdir -p models\n","\n","print(f\"PyTorch version: {torch.__version__}\")\n","print(f\"Device: {device}\")\n","\n","# Import other libraries\n","from PIL import Image\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import seaborn as sns\n","from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n","from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score, precision_score, recall_score\n","\n","# Configure plot display settings\n","sns.set(font_scale=1.4)\n","sns.set_style('white')\n","plt.rc('font', size=14)\n","%matplotlib inline\n","\n","# Add functions for training, visualisation and model\n","from src.utils import (\n","    NPYSegmentationDataset,\n","    make_dataloaders,\n","    apply_colormap,\n","    plot_sample_images,\n","    UNetBlock,\n","    UNet,\n","    train_segmentation_model,\n","    plot_triptychs_from_loader,\n","    find_representative_indices,\n","    plot_triptychs_from_loader_with_selection,\n","    plot_layer_outputs_from_loader,\n",")\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["Path(f\"experiments/{experiment_name}\").mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)"],"metadata":{"id":"n9bRcO8KkQ5A"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":345414,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849017092,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"UDqgnQuVBUxP","outputId":"ee6e3da6-eecc-484a-c05c-f0ca42712527"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Copying patches to the local storage...\n","Ready!\n"]}],"source":["print(\"Copying patches to the local storage...\")\n","if patches_from_merged_dataset:\n","    src = f\"{project_dir}/data/merged_patches_datasets/{patches_folder_name}\"\n","else:\n","    src = f\"{project_dir}/data/sites/{specific_site_name}/patches/{patches_folder_name}\"\n","dst = \"/content/patches\"\n","\n","shutil.copytree(src, dst)\n","print(\"Ready!\")\n","\n","OUT_DIR = dst"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":81,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849017211,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"c4l0YrGLgYO6","outputId":"1fa14405-4fa1-42c3-fded-c7bb02e68ce7"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Channels in patch: 30\n","Number of classes: 2\n"]}],"source":["import json\n","\n","with open(f\"{OUT_DIR}/metadata.json\") as f:\n","    meta = json.load(f)\n","\n","INPUT_CHANNELS = meta[\"n_bands_total\"]\n","NUM_CLASSES = meta[\"n_classes\"]\n","\n","print(f\"Channels in patch: {INPUT_CHANNELS}\\nNumber of classes: {NUM_CLASSES}\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"tyfmJGTmfJGz"},"source":["## ⏳ **Load and Process Data**"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":2950,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849020155,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"HjYcvu7jXifR","outputId":"09473a66-f72f-48da-ff6e-3bc7edde4fdf"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["train:  2000 patches →  125 batches/epoch\n","val  :   662 patches →   42 batches/epoch\n","test :   400 patches →   25 batches/epoch\n","\n","[train] img: (16, 30, 128, 128) torch.float32  mask: (16, 128, 128)  values: [0, 1, 255]\n","\n","[val] img: (16, 30, 128, 128) torch.float32  mask: (16, 128, 128)  values: [0, 1, 255]\n","\n","[test] img: (16, 30, 128, 128) torch.float32  mask: (16, 128, 128)  values: [0, 1, 255]\n","\n","✅  OK\n"]}],"source":["if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n","    loaders = make_dataloaders(OUT_DIR, batch_size=16, num_workers=2)\n","\n","    for split, loader in loaders.items():\n","        imgs, masks = next(iter(loader))\n","        print(f\"\\n[{split}] img: {tuple(imgs.shape)} {imgs.dtype}  \"\n","              f\"mask: {tuple(masks.shape)}  \"\n","              f\"values: {masks.unique().tolist()}\")\n","    print(\"\\n✅  OK\")"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":41,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849020197,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"ohNDRQJ7fQKi","outputId":"e16d7343-3a40-4d14-bafc-266ea150fb11"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Creating datasets...\n","Train dataset size: 2000\n","Validation dataset size: 662\n"]}],"source":["print(\"Creating datasets...\")\n","\n","train_dataset = NPYSegmentationDataset(\n","    root        = OUT_DIR,\n","    split       = \"train\",\n","    augmentation = True\n",")\n","\n","val_dataset = NPYSegmentationDataset(\n","    root        = OUT_DIR,\n","    split       = \"val\",\n","    augmentation = False\n",")\n","\n","print(f\"Train dataset size: {len(train_dataset)}\")\n","print(f\"Validation dataset size: {len(val_dataset)}\")"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":33,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849020232,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"RDv7OOy7huUW","outputId":"b1a76de1-2701-4849-b3b3-f3d9ff5477f8"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\n","DataLoaders created:\n","  Training batches:   125\n","  Validation batches: 42\n"]}],"source":["train_loader = loaders[\"train\"]\n","val_loader   = loaders[\"val\"]\n","\n","\n","print(f\"\\nDataLoaders created:\")\n","print(f\"  Training batches:   {len(train_loader)}\")\n","print(f\"  Validation batches: {len(val_loader)}\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"pSq4p-cfxULE"},"source":["## 👁️ **Visualise Training Samples**"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":1000},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":5437,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849025670,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"sIAyuELek-Z7","outputId":"d4fd87d5-189f-42bc-c9a6-f8e98f599aa1"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Visualising augmented training samples:\n"]},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 800x1200 with 6 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["# Get a batch from training loader to visualise augmented samples\n","print(\"Visualising augmented training samples:\")\n","\n","sample_images, sample_labels = next(iter(train_loader))\n","\n","# Convert tensors to numpy for visualisation\n","sample_images_np = sample_images.cpu()\n","sample_labels_np = sample_labels.cpu()\n","\n","\n","mask_cmap = ListedColormap([\n","    'black',   # unburned\n","    'red',     # burned\n","    'blue'     # ignore\n","])\n","\n","fig, axes = plt.subplots(3, 2, figsize=(8, 12))\n","\n","for i in range(3):\n","\n","    img = sample_images_np[i]\n","\n","    rgb = img[[7,6,5], :, :].permute(1,2,0).numpy()\n","    rgb = (rgb - rgb.min()) / (rgb.max() - rgb.min() + 1e-8)\n","\n","    mask = sample_labels_np[i].numpy()\n","\n","    mask_vis = mask.copy()\n","    mask_vis[mask_vis == 255] = 2\n","\n","    axes[i,0].imshow(rgb)\n","    axes[i,0].set_title(\"Image\")\n","    axes[i,0].axis(\"off\")\n","\n","    axes[i,1].imshow(mask_vis, cmap=mask_cmap, vmin=0, vmax=2)\n","    axes[i,1].set_title(\"Mask\")\n","    axes[i,1].axis(\"off\")\n","\n","# Legend\n","legend_elements = [\n","    Patch(facecolor='black', label='Unburned'),\n","    Patch(facecolor='red', label='Burned'),\n","    Patch(facecolor='blue', label='Ignore')\n","]\n","\n","fig.legend(\n","    handles=legend_elements,\n","    loc='lower center',\n","    ncol=3,\n","    bbox_to_anchor=(0.5, 0.02)\n",")\n","\n","plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0.05, 1, 1])\n","plt.savefig(f\"experiments/{experiment_name}/training_samples.png\")\n","plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"4aXgZo1qu_hb"},"source":["## 🏗️ **Build UNet Model**\n","\n","<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1Gu0WPFhU6GeVJUWPoR2KFYRZVI8rjo3p\" width=\"600\"/>"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":1000},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":3399,"status":"ok","timestamp":1780849029077,"user":{"displayName":"Evgenii Miasnikov","userId":"16558642990374440926"},"user_tz":-120},"id":"3xJjAmJHlOnr","outputId":"bfae18b4-683b-4478-ddb9-7992eec5bc3f"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["UNet Model Summary:\n","============================================================\n","----------------------------------------------------------------\n","        Layer (type)               Output Shape         Param #\n","===